data.title: Leona Lewis
data.meta_description: Leona Lewis. Soundtrack: Avatar - Aufbruch nach Pandora. Leona Lewis was born on 3 April 1985 in Islington, London, England, UK. She is a music artist and actress, known for Avatar - Aufbruch nach Pandora (2009), Freundschaft Plus (2011) and Sex and the City 2 (2010). She has been married to Dennis Jauch since 27 July 2019. They have one child.
